verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Jesus shall reign where’er the sun
Does its successive journeys run;
His kingdom spread from shore to shore,
‘Til moons shall wax and wane no more.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Let every creature rise and bring
His grateful honor to our King;
Angels descend with songs again,
And earth repeat the loud “Amen”!{/lang-eng}
